					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fiftynine" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1440737); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1440737&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610250148" alt="FiftyNine" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1440737)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fiftynine" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1440737); return false;" >FiftyNine</a></span> <span class="odate time_1460384408 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">11 Apr 2016 14:20</span>
